This is my vim config. To use it:

- Clone this:
    ```sh
    cd ~/.vim
    git clone git@github.com:idanarye/vimConfig.git
    ```

- Clone vim-plug:
    ```sh
    cd ~/.vim
    git clone https://github.com/junegunn/vim-plug.git
    ```

Add these lines to your .vimrc (replacing `/home/idanarye` with your the correct paths):
    ```vim
    let $MYVIMRC="/home/idanarye/.vim/vimConfig/_vimrc"
    source $MYVIMRC

    set runtimepath+=/home/idanarye/.vim/vim-plug/
    source /home/idanarye/.vim/vimConfig/custom_plugin_loading.vim
```
